(187, '103056569962014021509280597348454', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-plug text-success\'></i> Power Down Like a Pro</h4>\n               <p>Unplugging your chargers and gadgets when not in use can save you more than just a few pennies—it tackles \'vampire energy\' that sneaks up on your bills. Did you know standby power can account for up to 10% of your energy use? Go on a nightly unplugging spree!</p>\n               <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Energy efficiency is the cheapest, cleanest, and fastest way to cut energy costs.\' - Energy Saving Trust</p></blockquote>\n               <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: A quick win for every student’s budget!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(188, '1042202264052014120111480393049114', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-plug text-success\'></i> Power Down Like a Pro</h4>\n               <p>Unplugging your chargers and gadgets when not in use can save you more than just a few pennies—it tackles \'vampire energy\' that sneaks up on your bills. Did you know standby power can account for up to 10% of your energy use? Go on a nightly unplugging spree!</p>\n               <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Energy efficiency is the cheapest, cleanest, and fastest way to cut energy costs.\' - Energy Saving Trust</p></blockquote>\n               <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: A quick win for every student’s budget!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(189, '1042202264052014120111480393049114', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-shower text-primary\'></i> Shower Smarter, Save More</h4>\n               <p>Cutting your shower time by just 2 minutes can save gallons of hot water and keep your energy bills in check. Pair it with a low-flow showerhead, and you’re basically a water-saving superhero!</p>\n               <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Small changes in daily habits can lead to big savings over time.\' - Eco Warrior</p></blockquote>\n               <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Every drop counts—literally!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(190, '1042202264052014120111480393049114', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-lightbulb text-warning\'></i> Light Up Your Life Efficiently</h4>\n               <p>Swap out those old bulbs for LEDs—they last longer, use less energy, and give your room a vibe upgrade. Bonus: they’re perfect for late-night study sessions without the guilt of a high bill.</p>\n               <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'The future is bright with energy-efficient lighting.\' - Green Living</p></blockquote>\n               <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Shine smart, save smarter!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(191, '103056569962014021509280597348454', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-shower text-primary\'></i> Shower Smarter, Save More</h4>\n               <p>Cutting your shower time by just 2 minutes can save gallons of hot water and keep your energy bills in check. Pair it with a low-flow showerhead, and you’re basically a water-saving superhero!</p>\n               <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Small changes in daily habits can lead to big savings over time.\' - Eco Warrior</p></blockquote>\n               <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Every drop counts—literally!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(192, '1042202264052014120111480393049114', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-trophy text-warning\'></i> Energy Champion Status</h4>\n                   <p>A E rating? You’re killing it! Share your tips with housemates—maybe host a ‘low-energy living’ night. Keep it up with regular checks on your appliances and thermostat.</p>\n                   <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Leading by example is the best way to inspire change.\' - Sustainability Guru</p></blockquote>\n                   <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: You’re the MVP of energy saving!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(193, '103056569962014021509280597348454', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-lightbulb text-warning\'></i> Light Up Your Life Efficiently</h4>\n               <p>Swap out those old bulbs for LEDs—they last longer, use less energy, and give your room a vibe upgrade. Bonus: they’re perfect for late-night study sessions without the guilt of a high bill.</p>\n               <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'The future is bright with energy-efficient lighting.\' - Green Living</p></blockquote>\n               <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Shine smart, save smarter!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(194, '103056569962014021509280597348454', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-leaf text-success\'></i> Keep Your Green Streak Going</h4>\n                   <p>With a C rating, you’re on the right track! Maintain it by switching to LED lighting and boosting ventilation—stale air is so last semester. Small tweaks can keep your eco-cred high.</p>\n                   <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Consistency in small actions builds a sustainable future.\' - Climate Advocate</p></blockquote>\n                   <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Stay green, stay keen!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(195, '1042202264052014120111480393049114', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-history text-muted\'></i> Old House, New Tricks</h4>\n                   <p>Your England and Wales: 1900-1929 home has character, but it might need some love. Retrofit walls, roofs, and windows with insulation—think of it as a modern makeover. Draft stoppers are a cheap, DIY fix for now!</p>\n                   <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Old homes can learn new energy-saving habits.\' - RetroFit Pro</p></blockquote>\n                   <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Vintage vibes, modern savings!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(196, '103056569962014021509280597348454', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-tools text-info\'></i> Mid-Century Energy Boost</h4>\n                   <p>Built in England and Wales: 1950-1966, your place could use some cavity wall and loft insulation. It’s like putting a hat and coat on your house—keeps the heat in and bills down!</p>\n                   <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'A well-insulated home is a happy home.\' - Home Energy Guide</p></blockquote>\n                   <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Retrofit for retro cool!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(197, '1042202264052014120111480393049114', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-dollar-sign text-success\'></i> Slash Those Bills</h4>\n                           <p>Bills eating your pizza fund? Switch to a time-of-use tariff, turn off lights when you’re out, and do an energy audit—find where the cash leaks are. Every watt counts!</p>\n                           <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'Control your energy, control your wallet.\' - Money Saver</p></blockquote>\n                           <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: More money for late-night snacks!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
(198, '103056569962014021509280597348454', '<h4><i class=\'fas fa-thermometer-quarter text-warning\'></i> Warm Up Wisely</h4>\n                           <p>Is your heating a letdown? Layer up with socks and hoodies, grab a hot water bottle, and nag your landlord for a programmable thermostat. A quick boiler check can also turn up the heat!</p>\n                           <blockquote class=\'blockquote\'><p>\'A warm room starts with smart heating.\' - Cozy Living</p></blockquote>\n                           <small class=\'text-muted\'>Legend: Stay toasty without toasting your budget!</small>', 0, 0, 0, '2025-04-07 22:36:00'),
